Very nice open access and free botanical garden with some unique plants and well maintained.  It has some nice water features with a bridge and even some aquatic animals such as fish and turtles. Wonderful way to get out of the city air and off the concrete streets. It would be nice if there were some benches or chairs available to sit down and enjoy the peaceful atmosphere and fresh air.
